      This page uses ISO-8859-1 characters.  

	When you read this page, set Document Encoding into Western
	(Latin-1).  At Netscape, this option can be set from the
	"Document Encoding" menu, in the "Options"
	menu.




 à ... {`a}

 á ... {'a}

 â ... {^a}

 ã ... {~a}

 ä ... {"a}

 å ...{.a}

 ç ... {,c}

 æ ... {ae}

 ß ... {b}

    and so on.

